These giant ships are made in the shipyards around Mon Cala.
Fly near this spaceport if you want to land on Mon Cala.  If you're too far away, you won't be able to land.
Orbiting the oceanic planet of Mon Cala, the famous shipyards produce some of the highest quality starships in the Galaxy.
